OL,3,CWoman appears in court accused of the
OL,4,Cmurder of six-year-old boy
OL,6,FA woman has appeared in Swansea
OL,7,FMagistrates' Court charged with murder
OL,8,Fafter the death of a boy.
OL,10,FKarolina Zurawska, 41, from Gendros in
OL,11,FSwansea, is accused of killing 6-year-
OL,12,Fold Alexander Zurawski.
OL,14,FAlexander was found dead at a property
OL,15,Fin Cwm Du Close, Gendros on 29th
OL,16,FAugust.
OL,18,FZurawska has also been charged with
OL,19,Fattempted murder in connection with an
OL,20,Fincident involving a 67-year-old man
OL,21,Fon the same date, earlier in the day.
