OL,3,CWoman appears in court accused of the
OL,4,Cmurder of six-year-old boy
OL,6,FZurawska only spoke to confirm her
OL,7,Fname and date of birth and did not
OL,8,Fenter a plea. The magistrate referred
OL,9,Fthe case to the Crown Court.
OL,11,FShe is expected to appear at Swansea
OL,12,FCrown Court on Tuesday morning.
OL,14,FSouth Wales Police said the incident
OL,15,Fhad been "a tremendous shock to the
OL,16,Flocal community" and "a police
OL,17,Fpresence will be retained in the local
OL,18,Farea over the coming days in order to
OL,19,Fprovide advice and reassurance."
