OL,3,CWoman appears in court accused of the
OL,4,Cmurder of six-year-old boy
OL,6,FThe force confirmed they weren't
OL,7,Flooking for anyone else in connection
OL,8,Fto the incident.
OL,10,FAlexander's family described him as a
OL,11,F"very kind child" in a statement.
OL,13,F"He loved playing with his little
OL,14,Fsister and playing with his dog
OL,15,FDaisy," they said. "Alexander was
OL,16,Falways well behaved and never naughty.
OL,17,FHe was very clever and very mature for
OL,18,Fhis age. He had great understanding of
OL,19,Ffacts.
OL,21,F"He was amazing."
